#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:81
msgid "Welcome to Venu Pacific"
msgstr "Welkam long Venu Pacific"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:113
msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "Welkam"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:124
msgid ""
"A Debian-based desktop built for the Pacific Islands region, designed for "
"real conditions here: limited bandwidth, older hardware, and routine "
"cyclone/tsunami/earthquake exposure."
msgstr ""
"Wan desktop sistem we hemi base long Debian, we oli designem speseli blong "
"ol aelan blong Pasifik. Hem i stret long ol ril kondisen blong yumi olsem: "
"intanet i no strong tumas, ol kompiuta oli olfala, mo saeklon, tsunami mo "
"etkwek oli save hapen enitaem."

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:143
msgid "Language"
msgstr "Lanwis"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:147
msgid "English"
msgstr "Inglis"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:153
msgid "Bislama"
msgstr "Bislama"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:162
msgid "What's included"
msgstr "Wanem i stap insaed"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:65
msgid "Web browsing"
msgstr "Lukluk long intanet"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:66
msgid "Documents, spreadsheets, presentations"
msgstr "Ol dokumen, spreadsheet, presentesen"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:67
msgid "Image editing"
msgstr "Editim ol imej"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:70
msgid ""
"Offline Wikipedia and Pacific health/agriculture/disaster info. Works "
"with no internet connection"
msgstr ""
"Wikipedia we i no nidim intanet, mo infomesen long helt, fam, mo disasta "
"blong Pasifik, i save wok nomata sapos i no gat intanet"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:75
msgid "Install or remove software"
msgstr "Installem o rimuvum sofwea"

#: welcome-app/venu-pacific-welcome:187
msgid "Get Started"
msgstr "Statem"
